 and provides a unified interface.\n\n However, note that the user's current workspace does not have a skill-creator skill. We might need to create one? But the instructions say to use the skill-creator skill when creating a skill.\n\n Since we don't have the skill-creator skill, we can still create a skill by following the structure we see.\n\n Let's create a new skill directory: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/research`\n\n We'll create:\n   - SKILL.md\n   - scripts/ (with helper scripts)\n   - references/ (optional)\n\n But note: the user might not want a full skill. Alternatively, we can create a simple script that the main agent can use to spawn a research subagent.\n\n Given the ambiguity, let's create a skill that provides research capabilities by combining YouTube and NotebookLM.\n\n However, note that the user might not have set up the YouTube API key or NotebookLM. We should check.\n\n Let's check the .env file for YOUTUBE_KEY and NOTION_KEY (for NotebookLM? Actually, NotebookLM uses Google auth, not Notion).\n\n We see the .env file has:\n   NOTION_KEY\n\n But we don't see YOUTUBE_KEY.\n\n We can still create the skill and note the requirements.\n\n Alternatively, we can create a subagent that, when given a research topic, will:\n   1. Search YouTube for videos on the topic.\n   2. Extract transcripts.\n   3. Use NotebookLM to create a notebook and generate a report.\n\n But note: we are a subagent and we are to complete the task. We are not to create a long-running process.\n\n Given the time, let's create a skill that documents how to do research using the available tools.\n\n We'll create the SKILL.md for the research skill.\n\n Steps:\n\n 1. Create the directory.\n 2. Write the SKILL.md.\n\n Let's do it.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0ad9459cb33f4e5ea17660d9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/skills/research/{scripts,references}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":15040,"output":851,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15891,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774975314665,"responseId":"chatcmpl-94449ffc49d1f731"}}
