ws the Search First Rule and other OpenClaw guidelines\n\nThe research subagent skill is now ready to help with tasks like gathering information on topics, analyzing content from multiple sources, conducting deep research, and creating research reports or summaries. You can use it by specifying your research question/topic and preferred methods, and it will guide you through an appropriate research workflow."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":19942,"output":415,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20357,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774975538226,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8eb6c3d92818dcbc"}}
